as formal cooperative arrangements should register in person at the privileges desk in the cecil h green library during regular business hours monday through friday 8 00am to 5pm during evenings and weekend hours visitors may sign in at one of the green library portals and request a registration form to complete at that time detailed information for visitors is available here social sciences group menu back stanford university stanford california 94305 650 725 1064 terms of use copyright complaints
